NK041(di)007:3: rgyal sras tshe dbang rnam rgyal /
NK041(di)007:5: mtshan ldan bsod nams rgyal mtshan /
NK041(di)007:7: thugs sras kun bzang rnam rgyal /
NK041(di)007:8: man+d+rad+h+aaranas+autramarah gsang sngags mdo sngags rgya mtsho /
NK041(di)007:10: mnyam med tshe dbang nor bu /
NK041(di)007:13: manisamudrah mtshungs med ma ni mu dra /
NK041(di)007:14: kit+tid+h+wadzah 'gro mgon grags pa rgyal mtshan /
NK041(di)007:17: ab+hayad+harmut+tamasadrah 'jigs med chos mchog rgya mtsho /
NK041(di)007:18: saman+tab+hadrasam+pat+tihdrah kun bzang dpal 'byor rgya mtsho /
NK041(di)007:22: bshad sgrub bstan pa'i rgyal mtshan /
NK041(di)007:25: klong gsal dag snang las byung ba'i brda yig bum gzungs /
NK041(di)007:27: 'di gser lta bus bris nas bcug /
NK041(di)007:28: nyin mo bde legs mtshan bde legs //
NK041(di)007:29: nyi ma'i gung yang bde legs shing //
NK041(di)007:30: nyin mtshan rtag tu bde legs par //
NK041(di)007:31: dkon mchog gsum gyis bkra shis shog //
NK041(di)007:32: bsod nams ri bo bzhin du brtan pa dang //
NK041(di)007:33: brgyud 'dzin nyi zla bzhin du bsal ba dang //
NK041(di)007:34: snyan grags nam mkha' lta bur khyab gyur pa'i //
NK041(di)007:35: gsum mo des kyang deng 'dir bde legs shog //
NK041(di)007:36: lo brgya thub cing ston brgya mthong ba dang //
NK041(di)007:37: tshe ring nad med bde skyid phun sum tshogs //
NK041(di)007:38: theg pa mchog la nges par 'byung ba ste //
NK041(di)007:39: lnga po des kyang deng 'dir bde legs shog //
NK041(di)007:40: bstan pa'i dpal gyur bla ma'i zhabs pad brtan //
NK041(di)007:41: bstan 'dzin skyes bus sa steng yongs la khyab //
NK041(di)007:42: bstan pa'i sbyin bdag mnga' thang 'byor pa rgyas //
NK041(di)007:43: bstan pa yun ring gnas pa'i bkra shis shog /
NK041(di)007:44: chos rnams thams cad rgyu las byung //
NK041(di)007:45: de rgyu de bzhin gshegs pas gsungs //
NK041(di)007:46: rgyu las 'gogs pa gang yin pa //
NK041(di)007:47: dge sbyong chen pos 'di skad gsungs //
NK041(di)007:48: ye d+har+m+m+aa he tu pra b+ha b+aa he tun+te sh+aan+ta th+aa ga to h+ya wa data /
NK041(di)007:49: te sh+aany+tsa yo ni ro d+ha e wam b+aa d+ai ma h+aa sh+ra ma na ye s+w+aa h+aa /
NK041(di)007:57: am ah ka kha ga g+ha nga /
NK041(di)007:63: sha sha sa ha k+shah gter mdzod /
NK041(di)007:64: nipar bla ma'i sku gdung mchod chog las /
NK041(di)007:65: dus gsum sangs rgyas thams cad kyi ngo bor gyur
NK041(di)007:66: cing dmigs pa med pa'i thugs rje dang ldan pa
NK041(di)007:67: dpal ldan bla ma brgyud pa dang bcas pa rnams
NK041(di)007:68: dang / sangs rgyas dang byang chub sems dpa' thams cad bdag la dgongs su gsol //
NK041(di)007:69: bdag cag rnams kyis dkon mchog la mchod pa phul ba dang /
NK041(di)007:70: dge 'dun la bsnyen bkur bgyis pa dang /
NK041(di)007:71: 'byung po la gtor ma gtong ba dang /
NK041(di)007:75: sgom sgrub la sogs pa bsod nams dang ye shes
NK041(di)007:76: kyi tshogs ci bsags pa'i dge ba'i rtsa ba 'di
NK041(di)007:77: dag thams cad gcig tu bsdus shing bzlums te bsdoms
NK041(di)007:78: nas rigs kun khyab bdag 'dren mchog mtshungs med /
NK041(di)007:79: dpal ldan bla ma dam pa yab sras brgyud pa dang bcas pa rnams la 'bul bar bagyi'o //
NK041(di)007:80: phul bas bla ma dge ba'i bshes gnyen rnams kyi
NK041(di)007:81: thugs dgongs khyad par can rnams gong nas gong du
NK041(di)007:83: sa dang lam gyi rim pa'i spang bya dang gegs
NK041(di)007:84: dang sgrib par gyur pa ci mchis pa thams cad
NK041(di)007:85: byang zhing dag par gyur cig /
NK041(di)007:86: lam lnga sa bcu rim gyis bgrod nas bdag cag
NK041(di)007:87: la sogs pa sems can thams cad kyi don du
NK041(di)007:88: myur du mngon par rdzogs par 'tshang rgya bar gyur
NK041(di)007:89: cig / sems can thams cad kyi don gang la
NK041(di)007:90: gang 'dul gyi sprul pa'i sku'i mdzad pa rgyun mi
NK041(di)007:92: der yang sku tshe'i 'du byed bskal pa rgya mtshor
NK041(di)007:93: g.yo med du bstan cing ngo mtshar ba'i rnam par
NK041(di)007:94: thar pa mtha' yas pas bstan pa dang sems can
NK041(di)007:95: gyi don rlabs po che mdzad par gyur cig /
NK041(di)007:96: bdag cag rnams la'ang bla ma brten pa'i sgo nas bsags pa'i nyes pa sku la barngosa pa /
NK041(di)007:99: nyes pa gtam du brjod pa /
NK041(di)007:101: thugs sun phyung ba la sogs pa nyes pa'i tshogs
NK041(di)007:102: ci mchis pa thams cad byang zhing dag par gyur
NK041(di)007:103: cig / tshe rabs thams cad du yang dag pa'i dge ba'i bshes gnyen dang mjal bar gyur cig /
NK041(di)007:104: mjal nas kyang mnyes par byed par gyur cig /
NK041(di)007:105: mi mnyes pa skad cig kyang byed par ma gyur cig /
NK041(di)007:106: skye ba tshe rabs thams cad du dge ba'i bshes gnyen gyis rjes su 'dzin par gyur cig /
NK041(di)007:107: gzung du gtub par gyur cig /
NK041(di)007:108: gdams ngag dang rjes su bstan pas skyong bar gyur cig /
NK041(di)007:109: bskyong du gtud bar gyur cig /
NK041(di)007:110: tshe rabs thams cad du dge ba'i bshes gnyen mi brjed pa'i ting nge 'dzin thob par gyur cig /
NK041(di)007:111: dge ba'i bshes gnyen gyi rnam par thar pa la longs spyod par gyur cig /
